snippet.title: Skygard Arena - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Skygard Arena is a turn-based tactical RPG with a vibrant roster of MOBA-style Heroes. Assemble your squad, equip items and abilities, and outplay your opponents in fast-paced strategic battles. Discover the world of Skygard in a multi-campaign solo adventure, or fight in thrilling PvP matches! 

🐼 Pick 5 heroes between many!
🛡️ Customize them to build the best team!
⚔️ Fight in intense tactical battles!
🐱 Discover the world of Skygard and its various factions!

Wishlist us now on Steam ➡️ https://rb.gy/vrm8sm
